          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4 text-blue-600 text-2xl">üìÑ</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Streamlined Documentation</h3>
