          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4 text-orange-500 text-2xl">üìä</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Real-Time Tracking & Workflow Automation</h3>
